      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if a single dose is 400mg and i take it every 2 hours, i'm only taking 400mg at a time... wouldn't the amount in my blood stay pretty low and steady? i feel like if i wait 6 hours like you said, the pain is just gonna spike again and be way worse. isn't it better to just keep a consistent level in my system?",
